Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.01,0:01:52.97,Default,Tristepin,0,0,0,,ミﾞ、ミﾞスﾞゥゥ...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.64,0:02:14.54,Default,Amalia,0,0,0,,なんでいつもこういう状況に陥っちゃうわけ？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.15,0:02:17.77,Default,Evangelyne,0,0,0,,寄り道してばかりだからよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.77,0:02:21.34,Default,Evangelyne,0,0,0,,時間が豊富にあるなら、弱きを助け強きをくじくのもいいけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.34,0:02:25.26,Default,Tristepin,0,0,0,,ああ、でも俺たちはヒーローだ。\n弱いものを助けるのはヒーローの義務だぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.63,0:02:29.01,Default,Yugo,0,0,0,,その通りだよパンパン、ヒーローは世界を良くするためにいるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.35,0:02:33.60,Default,Evangelyne,0,0,0,,気持ちはわかるわ。でも悲劇的な話なんてそこら中に溢れてるのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.60,0:02:36.52,Default,Evangelyne,0,0,0,,何をすべきか考えなきゃ。最優先なのはなに？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.00,0:02:42.64,Default,Ruel,0,0,0,,わからん･･･何も考えられん･･･脳みそこんがりじゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.64,0:02:44.02,Default,Evangelyne,0,0,0,,ユーゴ、答えて！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.20,0:02:47.03,Default,Yugo,0,0,0,,最優先か･･･
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.03,0:02:49.70,Default,Yugo,0,0,0,,うーん、シノノメのドフスを見つけることかな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.70,0:02:51.15,Default,Evangelyne,0,0,0,,Well it doesn't look like it.ええ、順調とは言えないわ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.15,0:02:54.60,Default,Evangelyne,0,0,0,,出発してから数週間経つけど、まだ半分も来てないのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.60,0:02:56.47,Default,Evangelyne,0,0,0,,この調子じゃあと数週間はかかるわ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.47,0:02:58.26,Default,Evangelyne,0,0,0,,アダマイのことも考えてあげて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.62,0:03:02.98,Default,Evangelyne,0,0,0,,できる限り早く戻るって約束したでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.73,0:03:06.86,Default,Evangelyne,0,0,0,,みんながあなたの冒険に心血を注いでるのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.26,0:03:10.06,Default,Evangelyne,0,0,0,,それでもあなたが世界中の苦しみを解決したいっていうなら\n好きにすればいいわ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.06,0:03:13.82,Default,Evangelyne,0,0,0,,でもよければ、この任務が終わってからにしない？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.32,0:03:15.43,Default,Yugo,0,0,0,,僕･･･僕は･･･
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.05,0:03:20.99,Default,Yugo,0,0,0,,わかったよ、エヴァ。これからは任務に集中する
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.07,0:03:45.45,Default,Evangelyne,0,0,0,,あそこを見て！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.45,0:03:47.46,Default,Evangelyne,0,0,0,,地図に載ってるオアシスだわ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.87,0:03:49.66,Default,Tristepin,0,0,0,,水だ！！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.10,0:03:53.65,Default,Ruel,0,0,0,,あっちじゃ！水の流れる音が聞こえるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.65,0:03:54.87,Default,Tristepin,0,0,0,,ああ、あっちだ！入り口がある
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.59,0:03:57.98,Default,Yugo,0,0,0,,ちょっと！置いていかないでよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.84,0:04:12.83,Default,Tristepin,0,0,0,,これだよ、正にパラダイスだぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.87,0:04:22.86,Default,Ruel,0,0,0,,パンパン、認めるのは癪じゃがそうとしか言いようがないな･･･
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.54,0:04:26.78,Default,Tristepin,0,0,0,,水だーーー！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.78,0:04:37.51,Default,Bordegann,0,0,0,,立ち去れ、見知らぬものたちよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.51,0:04:41.07,Default,Bordegann,0,0,0,,私はボードガン、何人たりともこの泉の水を飲ませるわけにはいかない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.07,0:04:42.04,Default,Tristepin,0,0,0,,なんだって？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.04,0:04:43.26,Default,Tristepin,0,0,0,,なんで飲んじゃだめなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.45,0:04:53.21,Default,Ruel,0,0,0,,見逃してくれんかのぅ。ワシらはのどが渇いて死にそうなんじゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.51,0:04:55.64,Default,Bordegann,0,0,0,,確かにここは凄まじく暑いからな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.64,0:04:58.38,Default,Bordegann,0,0,0,,だが申し訳ない。飲ませるわけにはいかんのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.78,0:05:01.97,Default,Ruel,0,0,0,,Don't think I'll drink to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.85,0:05:09.60,Default,Yugo,0,0,0,,あのぉ、なんで飲んじゃだめなんですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.95,0:05:12.65,Default,Bordegann,0,0,0,,なぜ飲んではいけないか、だと？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.65,0:05:13.83,Default,Bordegann,0,0,0,,それは･･･
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.53,0:05:15.98,Default,Bordegann,0,0,0,,絶対に飲んではいけないからだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.98,0:05:18.98,Default,Ruel,0,0,0,,それじゃあちょっと納得はできんのう！若造！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.20,0:05:22.62,Default,Tristepin,0,0,0,,ああ、俺もリュエルと同感だぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.25,0:05:26.86,Default,Alia,0,0,0,,ダメーー！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.13,0:05:28.54,Default,Ruel,0,0,0,,ん？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.53,0:05:33.83,Default,Alia,0,0,0,,やめて、お願いだから
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.65,0:05:37.96,Default,Alia,0,0,0,,彼が失礼を。悪い人ではないのです
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.96,0:05:40.94,Default,Alia,0,0,0,,ただ･･･彼自身、ここで何をしているのかわからないのです
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.43,0:05:43.34,Default,Alia,0,0,0,,お水なら少しあります
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.71,0:05:46.87,Default,Alia,0,0,0,,どうぞ、お好きなだけ飲んでください
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.87,0:05:48.50,Default,Ruel,0,0,0,,ありがとう、お嬢さん
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.21,0:05:52.20,Default,Amalia,0,0,0,,女性と子供が先よ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.78,0:05:57.70,Default,Bordegann,0,0,0,,立ち去れ、見知らぬものよ。\n私はボードガン、何人――
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.70,0:06:00.78,Default,Alia,0,0,0,,ええ、ボードガン、わかってるわ。泉に用があって来たんじゃないのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.78,0:06:03.24,Default,Alia,0,0,0,,食べ物を持ってきたの
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.24,0:06:04.37,Default,Bordegann,0,0,0,,食べ物？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.80,0:06:08.42,Default,Bordegann,0,0,0,,なんて親切な。ありがとう、お嬢さん
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.10,0:06:17.71,Default,Alia,0,0,0,,今日は、ドライフルーツとシリアル、デザートにカルーガも
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.33,0:06:22.94,Default,Bordegann,0,0,0,,素晴らしい。カルーガは好物なんだ。良くわかったね
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.81,0:06:26.45,Default,Alia,0,0,0,,毎日来てるからね、ボードガン･･･
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.45,0:06:29.60,Default,Bordegann,0,0,0,,そうなのか？ところで･･･君の名前は？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.60,0:06:30.60,Default,Alia,0,0,0,,アリア･･･
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.26,0:06:33.10,Default,Alia,0,0,0,,私はアリアよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.10,0:06:36.04,Default,Bordegann,0,0,0,,アリア？素敵な名前だ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.04,0:06:37.90,Default,Bordegann,0,0,0,,じゃあ、ありがとう、アリア
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.31,0:06:54.26,Default,Alia,0,0,0,,また明日ね、ボードガン･･･
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.14,0:07:02.82,Default,Alia,0,0,0,,一緒にいらっしゃいますか？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.82,0:07:06.76,Default,Alia,0,0,0,,私の村はここからそれほど離れていないのです\n大したおもてなしもできませんけど･･･
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.10,0:07:29.86,Default,Alia,0,0,0,,村の泉は･･･あちらです
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.48,0:07:40.56,Default,Alia,0,0,0,,この辺りは旅人もほとんど訪れないのです\nしばらくこちらで外の話を聞かせてくださるとうれしいわ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.56,0:07:43.86,Default,Evangelyne,0,0,0,,そうしたいのはやまやまだけれど、長い旅の途中なのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.86,0:07:45.55,Default,Evangelyne,0,0,0,,あまり長居はできないの
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.55,0:07:49.15,Default,Alia,0,0,0,,せめて食べ物だけでも持っていってください\n南海岸への道は厳しいわ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.15,0:07:52.69,Default,Alia,0,0,0,,砂漠を横断するには、十分な食料が必要です
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.69,0:07:55.14,Default,Yugo,0,0,0,,うん！親切にありがとう！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.14,0:07:58.46,Default,Evangelyne,0,0,0,,アマリア、私はユーゴと行ってくるから、彼らをよろしく
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.94,0:07:59.90,Default,Evangelyne,0,0,0,,じゃあまた後で
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.64,0:08:14.38,Default,Ruel,0,0,0,,こら！老人には優しくせんか！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.38,0:08:18.59,Default,Orphan Iop,0,0,0,,ぼくはボードガン！この泉を守ってる！あっちへいけ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.96,0:08:25.58,Default,Ruel,0,0,0,,坊主、お情けをかけて今回は許してやろう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.75,0:08:28.74,Default,Ruel,0,0,0,,もう許さんぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.55,0:08:37.66,Default,Mama Pandawa,0,0,0,,いいかげんにしなさい！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.66,0:08:41.38,Default,Mama Pandawa,0,0,0,,すぐにやめなさい！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.79,0:08:44.30,Default,Mama Pandawa,0,0,0,,ごめんなさいね、旅の方。躾がなってなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.30,0:08:48.70,Default,Mama Pandawa,0,0,0,,食事をしたいなら、ローカの宿があるわ。ちょうど行くところだったの
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.70,0:08:51.06,Default,Mama Pandawa,0,0,0,,怒られる前におうちに帰りなさい！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.06,0:08:54.19,Default,Mama Pandawa,0,0,0,,その態度はなに！？今すぐあっちへ行きなさい！！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.30,0:08:58.00,Default,Ruel,0,0,0,,I think we've stumbled upon a “village de fous”.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.77,0:09:07.28,Default,Alia,0,0,0,,干し肉を少し入れましょう、おかずにいいわ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.28,0:09:10.58,Default,Yugo,0,0,0,,なぜボードガンは泉を守っているの？\n何か特別な事情でもあるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.79,0:09:14.50,Default,Alia,0,0,0,,呪いなの
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.35,0:09:18.90,Default,Yugo,0,0,0,,呪い？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.35,0:09:22.89,Default,Alia,0,0,0,,これは長くて悲しいお話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.89,0:09:24.38,Default,Alia,0,0,0,,ボードガンは私の恋人なの
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.38,0:09:29.03,Default,Alia,0,0,0,,私たちはみな、オグレストの混沌で飲み込まれてしまった島から来たの
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.03,0:09:31.86,Default,Alia,0,0,0,,ボードガンは放棄された村の話を聞きつけてきて
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.86,0:09:34.34,Default,Alia,0,0,0,,環境は厳しく、他から隔絶された土地だけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.34,0:09:37.50,Default,Alia,0,0,0,,私たちは新しく住処を見つけることが何より重要だった
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.91,0:09:43.84,Default,Alia,0,0,0,,彼はその場所を見つけて村を再建するため、\n遠征隊を率いて行ったわ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.84,0:09:47.45,Default,Alia,0,0,0,,でも２週間経っても音沙汰がなく、私たちは彼らを探すことにしたの
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.60,0:09:52.59,Default,Alia,0,0,0,,仲間は誰も見当たらず、ボードガンただ一人が残っていたわ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.59,0:09:54.58,Default,Alia,0,0,0,,呪われた泉のところよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.65,0:10:10.36,Default,Alia,0,0,0,,彼は半ば狂ってしまっていた
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.40,0:10:14.84,Default,Alia,0,0,0,,彼は記憶を失っていて、私のこともわからなくなっていた
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.84,0:10:18.12,Default,Alia,0,0,0,,何が起きたかはわからないけれど、\n私の愛が間違っていたとは思わないわ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.12,0:10:22.62,Default,Alia,0,0,0,,彼は泉を守ろうとしてる。\nあの泉が原因のひとつに違いないって確信してるの
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.69,0:10:28.63,Default,Alia,0,0,0,,それ以来ずっと、毎日食事を運んだりとか、お世話をしているの\n彼の記憶が戻ることを願って
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.63,0:10:32.61,Default,Alia,0,0,0,,村の人は、私が絶望しておかしくなっちゃったと思ってる\nでも必要とされる限りは待ち続けるつもりよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.48,0:10:36.22,Default,Alia,0,0,0,,私は･･･彼を見捨てないわ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.02,0:10:43.20,Default,Yugo,0,0,0,,記憶を取り戻すいい方法があるはずだよ･･･僕らが手伝うよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.20,0:10:44.71,Default,Evangelyne,0,0,0,,ユーゴ･･･
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.53,0:10:46.85,Default,Yugo,0,0,0,,うん、エヴァ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.85,0:10:47.94,Default,Yugo,0,0,0,,僕･･･
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.94,0:10:51.86,Default,Yugo,0,0,0,,ごめんアリア、僕ら緊急の任務の途中なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.86,0:10:54.15,Default,Yugo,0,0,0,,でも戻ってきて手伝うよ、約束する
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.15,0:10:55.21,Default,Yugo,0,0,0,,だよね、エヴァ？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.66,0:11:09.21,Default,Amalia,0,0,0,,アリアは可愛いけど、私に言わせればちょっとおばかさんね
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.21,0:11:12.18,Default,Amalia,0,0,0,,私だったら、ボードガンみたいな野蛮な男、\nそばに置いておくのは嫌だわ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.18,0:11:15.61,Default,Amalia,0,0,0,,I would've run off long ago to see if the grass was greener elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.61,0:11:18.10,Default,Ruel,0,0,0,,What were they thinking, burrowing in such a godforsaken place?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.10,0:11:20.30,Default,Ruel,0,0,0,,子供たちもおかしくなってしもうたんじゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.30,0:11:23.56,Default,Tristepin,0,0,0,,俺は彼女の気持ちがわかるぜ。恋は時に人を愚かにするものさ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.56,0:11:24.75,Default,Tristepin,0,0,0,,な？エヴァ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.83,0:11:31.15,Default,Evangelyne,0,0,0,,いいえ、違うわ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.50,0:11:35.75,Default,Tristepin,0,0,0,,え、歩きたくないのか？俺に運んで欲しいってことか？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.75,0:11:39.50,Default,Evangelyne,0,0,0,,いいえ、違うわ･･･彼らをこのままにはしておけない。戻りましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.50,0:11:40.82,Default,Tristepin,0,0,0,,何を言ってるんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.82,0:11:44.37,Default,Amalia,0,0,0,,戻る？なぜ？なにか忘れ物でもしたの？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.58,0:11:50.85,Default,Yugo,0,0,0,,ありがとう、エヴァ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.09,0:12:00.83,Default,Ruel,0,0,0,,どういうことか説明してくれんかの？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.20,0:12:08.36,Default,Evangelyne,0,0,0,,I suppose you have done some research...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.36,0:12:11.50,Default,Alia,0,0,0,,Yes, but we didn't find anything. Only Bordegann is left.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.50,0:12:14.60,Default,Alia,0,0,0,,The villagers that accompanied him disappeared without a trace.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.60,0:12:17.18,Default,Louca,0,0,0,,That cursed fountain's the one to blame, that's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.18,0:12:21.46,Default,Alia,0,0,0,,But as I told you, we don't know if it's the water or the place that's cursed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.46,0:12:25.34,Default,Evangelyne,0,0,0,,Well then we're going to study it stone by stone, there's bound to be a clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.34,0:12:27.20,Default,Yugo,0,0,0,,What kind of clue are we looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.20,0:12:32.33,Default,Ruel,0,0,0,,Anything that looks magical. A gemstone, runes, a stele.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.33,0:12:34.06,Default,Client 1,0,0,0,,You're forgetting something...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.60,0:12:35.88,Default,Client 1,0,0,0,,Bordegann.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.88,0:12:37.95,Default,Client 1,0,0,0,,He won't let you get near the fountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.95,0:12:41.50,Default,Client 2,0,0,0,,Yeah. We've already tried several times, we never succeeded.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.50,0:12:44.78,Default,Louca,0,0,0,,They're right. Bordegann is too strong. It's a lost cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.78,0:12:48.56,Default,Evangelyne,0,0,0,,Well it just so happens that we're specialists in lost causes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.56,0:12:51.39,Default,Yugo,0,0,0,,Yeah! That's even how you recognize heroes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.52,0:12:58.18,Default,Bordegann,0,0,0,,Get back, stranger! My name is Bordegann and I protect--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.18,0:13:02.90,Default,Alia,0,0,0,,I know, Bordegann, I know, I'm not interested in the fountain, I'm just bringing you something to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.90,0:13:03.94,Default,Bordegann,0,0,0,,Something to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.61,0:13:07.84,Default,Alia,0,0,0,,...and your favorite dessert: a calouga.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.55,0:13:09.81,Default,Bordegann,0,0,0,,A calouga!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.81,0:13:10.92,Default,Amalia,0,0,0,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.92,0:13:12.76,Default,Tristepin,0,0,0,,Yeah! Ready to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.76,0:13:17.86,Default,Evangelyne,0,0,0,,Grovy! The point is not to fight him, but to immobilize him and find some clues.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.86,0:13:19.50,Default,Tristepin,0,0,0,,Oh, come on, I was just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.50,0:13:20.40,Default,Amalia,0,0,0,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.38,0:13:25.41,Default,Bordegann,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.41,0:13:26.37,Default,Bordegann,0,0,0,,What in the...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.37,0:13:27.86,Default,Amalia,0,0,0,,Your turn, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.47,0:13:32.58,Default,Yugo,0,0,0,,We've got to check every nook and cranny.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.58,0:13:33.66,Default,Bordegann,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.66,0:13:34.62,Default,Bordegann,0,0,0,,What in the...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.62,0:13:36.44,Default,Alia,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry, Bordegann.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.00,0:13:43.99,Default,Bordegann,0,0,0,,No! The fountain! You must not get near it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.86,0:13:58.54,Default,Bordegann,0,0,0,,Villains! You will taste my wrath!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.86,0:14:19.09,Default,Ruel,0,0,0,,He's a tough one, that's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.09,0:14:22.71,Default,Tristepin,0,0,0,,Say, Eva. Couldn't I use my sword? Just a little bit, to see if...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.71,0:14:24.08,Default,Evangelyne,0,0,0,,Grovy, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.08,0:14:27.04,Default,Amalia,0,0,0,,Well, at least tomorrow he'll have forgotten everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.04,0:14:29.14,Default,Evangelyne,0,0,0,,Well, we'll try something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.14,0:14:30.39,Default,Bordegann,0,0,0,,Marriage?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.00,0:14:33.14,Default,Alia,0,0,0,,Yes, {\i1}our{\i0} marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.14,0:14:35.51,Default,Alia,0,0,0,,Come on, hurry up, the mayor is waiting for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.51,0:14:37.74,Default,Bordegann,0,0,0,,Yes, miss! Err... Alia!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.74,0:14:39.70,Default,Bordegann,0,0,0,,One moment, I'm going to find my spear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.99,0:14:48.97,Default,Bordegann,0,0,0,,Uh, haven't I forgotten something? Now what was it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.97,0:14:51.80,Default,Alia,0,0,0,,Come on, Bordegann! We're going to be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.80,0:14:53.15,Default,Bordegann,0,0,0,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.94,0:14:57.30,Default,Bordegann,0,0,0,,Get back, stranger, nobody must get near this fountain!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.25,0:15:02.58,Default,Evangelyne,0,0,0,,Well, Grovy, what was your plan again?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.80,0:15:11.74,Default,Bordegann,0,0,0,,Oh! A calouga!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.48,0:15:22.14,Default,Tristepin,0,0,0,,This is how my master got me out of a well that I had hidden in to sulk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.27,0:15:26.14,Default,Tristepin,0,0,0,,He's biting! He's biting, come help!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.81,0:15:30.50,Default,Ruel,0,0,0,,It's a big one, a real big one!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.76,0:15:32.11,Default,Tristepin,0,0,0,,All together!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.05,0:15:40.01,Default,Evangelyne,0,0,0,,Well, Yugo, what was your idea again?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.46,0:15:44.70,Default,Ruel,0,0,0,,...and your favorite dessert: a calouga!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.70,0:15:48.13,Default,Bordegann,0,0,0,,My favorite? Really? But... but how do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.70,0:15:52.99,Default,Ruel,0,0,0,,Oh it's a very long story, but I can tell you about it, if you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.45,0:15:57.02,Default,Bordegann,0,0,0,,With pleasure, stranger. I love stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.02,0:15:59.22,Default,Bordegann,0,0,0,,At least... I-I think I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.22,0:16:01.96,Default,Yugo,0,0,0,,Ruel can talk for whole days without stopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.32,0:16:04.90,Default,Ruel,0,0,0,,A treasure like you've never seen!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.90,0:16:09.86,Default,Ruel,0,0,0,,Kamas by the hundreds, by the thousands! Ha, I believed I was in Enutrof's heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.86,0:16:14.38,Default,Ruel,0,0,0,,Alas, yeah, alas...\N...managed to steal from me. Such boldness!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.38,0:16:17.86,Default,Ruel,0,0,0,,Luckily, they were lead by a boss as ugly and stupid as my great-grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.86,0:16:19.65,Default,Ruel,0,0,0,,I say luckily, because, this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.65,0:16:23.26,Default,Ruel,0,0,0,,I had skimped a bit on the costs, and my steed wasn't of the highest grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.26,0:16:28.26,Default,Ruel,0,0,0,,Anyway, had it been a matter of speed...\N...So I said to him: "Do you take me for a bank or what?"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.26,0:16:30.98,Default,Ruel,0,0,0,,"This shovel isn't even worth the earth that soils it!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.98,0:16:35.62,Default,Ruel,0,0,0,,"You think you can scam me, kiddo, but I wouldn't put Kamas on it."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.62,0:16:41.82,Default,Ruel,0,0,0,,With a man of my rank... it was a bold move. And in such cases, there's only one solution: you don't let go of anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.82,0:16:47.10,Default,Ruel,0,0,0,,I look him straight in the eyes and I say to him: "See, in this world there's two kinds of people, my friend:
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.10,0:16:50.10,Default,Ruel,0,0,0,,those who pay, and those who get paid!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.10,0:16:51.42,Default,Ruel,0,0,0,,Hey! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.63,0:17:01.09,Default,Ruel,0,0,0,,"You pay!"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.78,0:17:05.05,Default,Tristepin,0,0,0,,Hands off my Eva!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.65,0:17:11.38,Default,Bordegann,0,0,0,,Who are you? What are you doing in my room?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.64,0:17:16.38,Default,Client 2,0,0,0,,We told you so: not gonna work. We've already tried everything to get him out of there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.22,0:17:24.79,Default,Client 1,0,0,0,,Yeah... Hope is just an illusion. And we stopped having illusions long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.39,0:17:27.98,Default,Tristepin,0,0,0,,By the way, what are these critters?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.98,0:17:31.17,Default,Alia,0,0,0,,We don't know. They were here when we arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.17,0:17:34.22,Default,Alia,0,0,0,,If they could talk, they could tell us what really happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.08,0:17:36.40,Default,Tristepin,0,0,0,,They're really funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.60,0:17:37.89,Default,Alia,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.89,0:17:40.57,Default,Alia,0,0,0,,Without them, I think I would've lost all hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.56,0:17:45.12,Default,Evangelyne,0,0,0,,You're right! There's always hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.12,0:17:48.31,Default,Evangelyne,0,0,0,,We'll start over again from the beginning. Here's what we're gonna do...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.68,0:17:51.60,Default,Bordegann,0,0,0,,What's your name, stranger?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.60,0:17:53.25,Default,Alia,0,0,0,,Alia, my name is--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.25,0:17:55.95,Default,Amalia,0,0,0,,Help! Somebody!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.95,0:17:59.42,Default,Alia,0,0,0,,Oh no! Someone's being attacked! Quick! Let's go check!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.17,0:18:06.47,Default,Amalia,0,0,0,,Help! Somebody!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.55,0:18:16.54,Default,Yugo,0,0,0,,I'll handle him. Take care of the fountain!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.28,0:18:39.50,Default,Alia,0,0,0,,Bubulle!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.50,0:18:42.10,Default,Alia,0,0,0,,That's Bubulle, one of the villagers that disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.10,0:18:45.35,Default,Evangelyne,0,0,0,,Huh? What happened? Did anyone see anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.42,0:18:57.24,Default,Evangelyne,0,0,0,,The gemstones, at the bottom of the fountain, take them all out of the water, quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.50,0:19:07.34,Default,Alia,0,0,0,,It's working!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.34,0:19:15.50,Default,Bordegann,0,0,0,,I've... understood... your... intentions... it's... the fountain... you're after!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.24,0:20:17.91,Default,Bordegann,0,0,0,,No, you must not get near the fountain!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.09,0:20:25.99,Default,Bordegann,0,0,0,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.85,0:20:33.06,Default,Bordegann,0,0,0,,The water serpent, I remember it. We're doomed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.48,0:20:43.03,Default,Alia,0,0,0,,Bordegann, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.86,0:20:52.42,Default,Evangelyne,0,0,0,,Yugo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.42,0:20:56.79,Default,Evangelyne,0,0,0,,You have to strike the fountain! Now! With full power!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.14,0:21:46.43,Default,Client 1,0,0,0,,It's too beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.70,0:21:56.56,Default,Bordegann,0,0,0,,I don't remember a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.56,0:21:59.05,Default,Bordegann,0,0,0,,It's as if I was asleep all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.05,0:22:01.82,Default,Bordegann,0,0,0,,I... I don't know how to thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.48,0:22:04.41,Default,Evangelyne,0,0,0,,Seeing you two reunited is enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.41,0:22:06.62,Default,Evangelyne,0,0,0,,You reminded me of what it means to be a "hero".
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.62,0:22:08.98,Default,Tristepin,0,0,0,,You know you're pretty nice as a zeroine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.35,0:22:11.97,Default,Evangelyne,0,0,0,,Heroes are there to make the world a nicer place, aren't they?
